dmca.title:
Google Removal Complaint: Section 18C of Australia's Racial Discrimination Act
of 19
dmca.body:
On May 5, 2006, Google received notice of a site in the Google search results
that allegedly violates Section 18C of Australia's Racial Discrimination Act
of 1975. In response to this complaint, Google removed the site from
www.google.com.au.
